                     <interp inst="t18210912-177-person1806" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am beadle of Hackney. I was fetched and took the prisoner in custody - found two shillings and three halfpence in his pocket, and a key which opened the desk - he said it was the key of his box, and that he had no money about him.</p>
               <p>MR. STARKEY. The money is mine.</p>
